<td style="vertical-align: middle; padding-right: 0.4em;"><span title="'A' in the Malayalam script"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f7/Malayalam.svg/40px-Malayalam.svg.png" width="40" height="28" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f7/Malayalam.svg/60px-Malayalam.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f7/Malayalam.svg/80px-Malayalam.svg.png 2x" /></span></td>
<td style="vertical-align: middle;"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"><a href="Malayalam_language" title="Malayalam language" class="mw-redirect">Malayalam</a> is written in a <a href="Malayalam_script" title="Malayalam script" class="mw-redirect">non-Latin script</a>. Malayalam text used in this article is transliterated into the Latin script according to the <a href="ISO_15919" title="ISO 15919">ISO 15919</a> standard.</span></td>
