<td><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Mal_0.png" class="image"><img alt="൦" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/69/Mal_0.png" width="21" height="21" /></a></td>
<td>൧</td>
<td>൨</td>
<td>൩</td>
<td>൪</td>
<td>൫</td>
